specimen examined.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="10" pageNumber="77">
CHINA. Hebei Province: Chengde City, Xinglong County, chestnut plantation, 
<geoCoordinate direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="15" value="40.36222">40°21'44&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate direction="east" orientation="longitude" precision="15" value="117.858055">117°51'29&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
